# Exclude secrets/credentials from Google Antigravity (and other Gemini-based tools)
# AI context. `.aiexclude` is the Google-standard exclusion file (Gemini Code Assist,
# Android Studio); it uses .gitignore syntax. See also the sibling .antigravityignore.
# This hides files from the agent's indexer; it is not a hard security boundary.
.env
.env.*
.envrc
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/id_rsa*
**/id_ed25519*
secrets/
